731
00:52:44.870 --> 00:52:46.413
<i>just trying to save</i>
<i>themselves.</i>

732
00:52:46.496 --> 00:52:52.586
<i>♪ ♪</i>

733
00:52:52.669 --> 00:52:54.838
<i>- Seeing people come in.</i>
