00:56:30.220 --> 00:56:32.639
- This way. please.
[baby cries]

797
00:56:32.722 --> 00:56:34.432
You're okay.

798
00:56:34.516 --> 00:56:36.059
Thank you.

799
00:56:37.894 --> 00:56:39.938
<i>- Because I had the paper</i>
