800
00:56:40.021 --> 00:56:41.106
<i>a soldier called.</i>

801
00:56:41.189 --> 00:56:43.608
<i>He said. "Okay. you can come."</i>

802
00:56:43.691 --> 00:56:46.152
He said.
"You are in safe hands."

803
00:56:46.236 --> 00:56:49.155
