842
01:00:31.377 --> 01:00:32.587
That was a vehicle.

843
01:00:32.670 --> 01:00:34.422
improvised explosive device.
you know.

844
01:00:34.505 --> 01:00:36.883
where you can just pack
so much explosive

845
01:00:36.966 --> 01:00:38.009
into those things.

846
01:00:38.092 --> 01:00:39.260
[gunshots]

