912
01:04:40.835 --> 01:04:43.796
<i>there was gunfire</i>
<i>that erupted.</i>

913
01:04:43.879 --> 01:04:45.464
<i>- I heard rounds going off.</i>

914
01:04:45.548 --> 01:04:49.385
